description:
In Mega-City One, the Judges are the law – acting as judge, jury, and executioner. But how do the citizens really feel about a system where they are powerless?

America Jara and Bennett Beeny grow up as best friends, living a fairly trouble-free life in a dangerous city… bar the odd encounter with a Judge. Time draws them apart, and when they are brought back together, Beeny is a successful singer and America has become involved with a terrorist organisation – with the Judges in its sights!

Written by John Wagner (A History of Violence) with art by Colin MacNeil (Judge Dredd: The Chief Judge’s Man) this dark and complex tale is a true 2000 AD classic!

Reprints the following stories:

  • America (Judge Dredd Megazine 1.01 - 1.07)
  • Fading of the Light (Judge Dredd Megazine 3.20 - 3.25)
  • Cadet (Judge Dredd Megazine 250 - 252)
name: America

description: The Thinker is destroyed and the world is in chaos, but Logan wants nothing to do with it. But the world isn't done with him yet and when the lives of Jessica and his son Jaq are put in jeopardy, Logan must once again don his armor. LOGAN'S RUN: AFTERMATH continues Logan's epic journey as he races towards an uncertain destiny..

When Megamind accidentally zaps Minion with his new mind-altering device, Minion turns from good to super evil. No longer satisfied with sidekick status, Minion leaves Megamind to start his own criminal empire. Will Megamind reverse the effects before Minion becomes Metro City’s new criminal kingpin? Or will evil prevail…again?
name: Bad Minion! Bad!, All The Best Toys, Minion's Day Off

description: Luke Skywalker and Princess Leia face off against Darth Vader over an ancient artifact of legendary power! Deep in the swamplands of the planet Mimban lies a powerful crystal, capable of giving its possessor such mastery over the Force as to be nearly invincible. In the right hands, it could save the galaxy. In the wrong hands, it could destroy it! With the explosion of the first Death Star still reverberating through the cosmos, Luke and Leia will find that the war they thought they won was only a battle, and that the dark side of the Force still stalks the galaxy. This hardcover is available only through Direct Market retail outlets, each volume's print run is limited to initial orders and will not be reprinted.
name: Splinter of the Mind's Eye

description: In hiding for generations, the evil Sith have waited for the precise moment to reveal themselves and take vengeance upon the Jedi Order. But in the final days before the Trade Federation blockade of the planet Naboo sets into motion the Sith plan for the overthrow of the Republic, the scheming Sith Lord Darth Sidious becomes concerned about the potential interference by the criminal syndicate Black Sun, a vast and powerful organization feared throughout the galaxy. Sidious cannot allow anything or anyone to hinder his purpose, and so he unleashes his merciless apprentice, the death-dealing destroyer, Darth Maul, to eradicate his adversaries—as only a master of the dark side can! Star Wars: Darth Maul is the first-ever graphic-novel adventure of the ultimate Sith enforcer, an explosive tale of intrigue, mystery, and blistering action.
name: TPB

Aqualad, Robin, Kid Flash, Superboy and Miss Martian are ready for their first mission as a team. To get to know each other better, they decide to trade stories around the campfire, revealing how they all started as crimefighters. Will this bring them together or underscore their differences?
name: What's the Story

description: The discovery of the remains of some Neanderthals in a cave in France unleashes primal instincts in Java, and he   attacks Professor Maubert , author of the discovery , during a conference. When Maubert is killed in unclear circumstances , Martin is called upon to defend the innocence of his friend, beacause suspect s have fallen on him.
name: Delitto nella preistoria

description: After having cleared Java from the charge of murdering professor Maubert, Martin Mystère is ready to face a new adventure, beginning with a secret document from the Vatican Archives. The text proves that, in 1140, an Indian American sank near Cadiz carrying a message for Pope Onofrio: The Secret of the Fountain of Eternal Youth. These days, Martin and Professor Von Hansen want to discover the hidden truth of this story.
name: L'uomo che scoprì l'Europa

description: The mission of Mystère and Von Hansen in the swamps of the Everglades , Florida , in search of the mythical kingdom of Prester John and the fabled Fountain of Youth , clashes first with the ambitions of the old millionaire Henry De Leon , then with a few unexplained incidents . Finally , Martin and Java are facing a group of sinister characters dressed as Spanish conquistadores .
name: La fonte della giovinezza

description: The expedition of Martin and Java in Florida has a dramatic result : Von Hansen disappeared in the collapse which destroyed the Fountain of Youth , but , at the end of history , Martin has reasons to believe that his friend survived in some way. The Bermuda Triangle is the location of the  new adventure , which will see Martin and Java dealing with a band of modern pirates .
name: Il Triangolo delle Bermude

description: A sinister link connects the unexplained disappearance of a boat disappeared in the Bermuda Triangle and the sinking of the " Lusitania " , the U.S. ship sunk by a German submarine in 1915 , with no apparent reason . Martin Mystere is grappling with two classic puzzles of the past , the solution of which will put more of those mysteries than those that it wil answer .
name: Il segreto del Lusitania

description: In New York City a mysterious killer sucks blood to his victims as a vampire and then kills them using a knife with a wooden blade . Inspector Travis , leading the investigation , asks for help to Martin Mystère and together they discover one of the huts of the assassin ...
name: Un vampiro a New York

description: The circle tightens around Herman Strauss, the Murderer with the dagger, or the mysterious serial killer terrorizing New York. Mystère will find himself face to face with the man who embodies one of the key figures of horror fiction: a true vampire. But Herman Strauss is not simply a monster: he ' s a victim of a curse, who lives his condition with despair and anguish. A condition that he will find intolerable in the a dramatic final climax.
name: La maledizione
